#lang scribble/doc
@(require scribble/manual)

@title{Modern Macros: a talk given at PADL 2023}

@author{Robby Findler}

Use @centered{@tt{raco pkg install modern-macros-talk}} to install the
package containing the talk's code and @centered{@tt{racket -l
 modern-macros-talk}} to run the talk. The source code can be found
by entering @onscreen{File|Open Require Path...} menu item in DrRacket
and entering @tt{modern-macros-talk/main} in the resulting dialog.
